        {
          "reviewTitle": "A cushion that offers mature skin a dewy glow!!",
          "reviewText": "I bought two shades Ivory and Petal one is more my winter shade and one is more my spring/summer shade but either way it\u2019s dewy glowy and easy to apply and carry with you anywhere including a plane! Doesn\u2019t spill because it\u2019s a cushion (we need more cushions in our lives) great for dry mature skin. See my before and after pics.",
