        {
          "reviewTitle": "Convenient Makeup for Everyday Use",
          "reviewText": "It is nice, but make sure to use a primer and setting powder. The first day I used it, I did not use a primer or setting powder and my face was soooo shiny and there were imprints on my phone. The color was a perfect match and I did not have to return for a different color. This is a super convenient makeup for everyday use but it is only medium coverage and does not have as much Color Correcting as I would like.",
