        {
          "reviewTitle": "Great Foundation",
          "reviewText": "I love this foundation. It is very lightweight and buildable. Every prestige brand I have used builds up in my pores, this foundation does not. It is long-lasting and wears well in the hot/dry climate that I live in. I have sensitive skin, and this foundation did not make me break out or develop a rash. I will buy this again.",
